M||titl|Use Set/Map for O(1) Lookups
M||impa|lo-md
M||impa|O(n) to O(1)
M||tags|javascript, set, map, data-structures, perf
M||tx|---
M|Use |tx|Convert arrays to Set/Map for repeated membership checks.
M|Use |**In|**
M|Use |tx|```ts
M|Use |tx|const allowedIds = ['a', 'b', 'c', ...]
M|Use |tx|items.filter(item => allowedIds.includes(item.id))
M|Use |tx|```
M|Use |**Co|**
M|Use |tx|```ts
M|Use |tx|const allowedIds = new Set(['a', 'b', 'c', ...])
M|Use |tx|items.filter(item => allowedIds.has(item.id))
M|Use |tx|```